title: Week 5 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap MNF, give key injury updates, talk what players have their stock up and break down how they would redraft the 1st Round of fantasy. Plus, Eric Moody joins to tell us who to target on the waiver wire.
